data.description: Welcome to the prestigious gated community of Wortham Oaks! This impressive 2-story home is where luxury living meets tranquility. As soon as you walk through the front door you are greeted with natural light and an open concept. The large kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, white cabinets, gas cooking, granite island and countertops, making it perfect for the chef in your home. There is a separate dining room ideal for hosting all the holiday gatherings. The primary suite is located downstairs and includes a large full bath ensuite, equipped with separate tub/shower, double vanity and walk in closet. The second floor hosts a large loft perfect for a second living room or games room along with the other 3 bedrooms and secondary bath. Enjoy the serene backyard with the oversized covered patio after a long day. Save school travel time to the new middle school that is currently being built in the neighborhood to adjoin the elementary school. Close to 35, 1604 and Randolph.
